{"tid":435850,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"（火影世界第一）一人幾個最鐘意既角色","createTime":"2017-10-14T15:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T03:33:27.000Z","uid":116214,"like":7,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e8d57741f9149be6a9c5dda95d8c5fea5ed9f5c7","tid":435850,"uid":116214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:53:52.000Z","msg":"講埋原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先<br />\n<br />\n鼬：果時第一次見佢出須佐勁好j，雖然出完就死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 作者寫得佢太神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我愛羅：睇到佢又比成條既人排斥，到做左風景，之後再成為聯合軍大隊長，真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班：一出場太有霸氣，令到聯合軍果種無助感，冇咩boss做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n柱間：佢地技能全部都好型，完全表現出忍者之神既果種強大，樹界降誕，五重羅生門，千手佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實自來也，水門，帶土都好鐘意...不能盡錄"},{"pid":"acf1482f58fa301b9cf7506a1d5e437d2eedef3a","tid":435850,"uid":25194,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"三代"},{"pid":"8bb1d5cf046583cc4c3f2f879161a52ab62248f2","tid":435850,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三代</blockquote><br />\n識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69315b8f07450329b77ce9a4880d37b7665cbb3","tid":435850,"uid":32298,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"一樂大叔"},{"pid":"fd5c40204398aaa7d1a77c1d91bdb3ebf5396a3f","tid":435850,"uid":116214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三代</blockquote><br />\n識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解鐘意？<br />\n<br />\n我覺得三代都唔錯，只係一開始作者未吹到咁大，今人覺得佢係都度，忍界大戰佢作用比一，二，四代分分鐘仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edaf2ad543e2bc623b75f72fd5b9c384c28c7fa1","tid":435850,"uid":116214,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一樂大叔</blockquote><br />\n我到依家都覺得佢隱藏緊實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800f24514b8df3b034c38522c8690181ca9ad7c0","tid":435850,"uid":71343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:02:24.000Z","msg":"凱<br />\n鼬<br />\n鬼狡<br />\n女水影"},{"pid":"b2f4e133b204713db223ea34f9912f85e3d9cd62","tid":435850,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一樂大叔</blockquote><br />\n我到依家都覺得佢隱藏緊實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實可能佢先係主角呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4db251a4a386b36c4dfea211f3c88d87e43197d","tid":435850,"uid":139613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:07:34.000Z","msg":"迪達拉"},{"pid":"10f91ab4482fa9193ee22865c8078273ef5fd451","tid":435850,"uid":136119,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"鼬同佐助<br />\n同鳴人成家<br />\n小櫻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身以前好唔中意佐助 覺得係佢害死鼬同死中二病 但諗諗下其實佢都只係無知 而鼬既死係本身佢自已一早預左 有埋劇本自己點死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你見佐助知道左真相之後喊到on99就知佢有幾中意哥哥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bcd292a827a40ef8e4adfd6226abbb172007c04","tid":435850,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:23:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三代</blockquote><br />\n識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點解鐘意？<br />\n</span><br />\n我覺得三代都唔錯，只係一開始作者未吹到咁大，今人覺得佢係都度，忍界大戰佢作用比一，二，四代分分鐘仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歷代最強火影喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a2677139ae2ca01f8d7e9efaae5990d5529049","tid":435850,"uid":57776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:32:56.000Z","msg":"大蛇丸<br />\n集妖氣，邪氣，霸氣既角色<br />\n大部分招式都同蛇有關，幾特別"},{"pid":"82e4fcadd1a7954b23d6912a18f757bc1dd0e51b","tid":435850,"uid":38391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:34:48.000Z","msg":"雛田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好怕羞但係好專一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n花火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edac8b9edab67a226336774e45abf8596b8d609","tid":435850,"uid":60539,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:46:06.000Z","msg":"帶土<br />\n果種對愛既執著<br />\n盲目幼稚既執著係最純最真既愛<br />\n成套漫畫講愛情最多係佢<br />\n同埋啲招式仲正<br />\n有自己既毒撚異空間世界<br />\n唔開心可以入去靜下<br />\n又有柱間細胞出木遁<br />\n空間扭曲配火盾/暗器<br />\n手心既黑棒<br />\n其實火影每個角色都勁有個人風格<br />\n但係我最中意都係帶土啲招式"},{"pid":"9b6c6ff0803a9076e7c75b23480c32c0735d13d5","tid":435850,"uid":46769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:48:13.000Z","msg":"竟然冇人講鹿丸"},{"pid":"cc80d4303b26e0fefab755da4acab1dad888be0c","tid":435850,"uid":27396,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:51:12.000Z","msg":"水門冇人講，好打都有限"},{"pid":"cee6009d0ad219a528b3f4b95d44134e2ac162d3","tid":435850,"uid":75547,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:51:32.000Z","msg":"自來也"},{"pid":"aeb3c8d82229d976277179a51831676b7ffd736e","tid":435850,"uid":129304,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/005119_bca54c409dd95f8eb17b36d0661178a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F005119_bca54c409dd95f8eb17b36d0661178a6.jpg&h=39728738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為左保護條村  明知會死都照開八門 <br />\n同埋  真係好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2262df6ce45070147ec4ce8b71e427360ba9f0b2","tid":435850,"uid":148611,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:05:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自來也</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同好 <br />\n阻止唔到大蛇丸變衰<br />\n師父死係自已好友大蛇丸到<br />\n最愛鋼手 唔鐘意佢<br />\n自已徒弟水門又早死 無力阻止<br />\n最後又死係自已徒弟長門手上<br />\n自來也人生表面上係三忍好威， 其實佢成個人生都充滿左無力感。。。。 有好多事情佢都無能力改變個結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁先係最痛苦<br />\n <br />\n最後死係深海中， 塵土轉生都無佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係我覺得最有血有肉的角色"},{"pid":"94e7f6d5a6e0d988764a4994a31ea8b3dd60b295","tid":435850,"uid":116214,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:48:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帶土<br />\n果種對愛既執著<br />\n盲目幼稚既執著係最純最真既愛<br />\n成套漫畫講愛情最多係佢<br />\n同埋啲招式仲正<br />\n有自己既毒撚異空間世界<br />\n唔開心可以入去靜下<br />\n又有柱間細胞出木遁<br />\n空間扭曲配火盾/暗器<br />\n手心既黑棒<br />\n其實火影每個角色都勁有個人風格<br />\n但係我最中意都係帶土啲招式</blockquote><br />\n其實點解佢唔復活琳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1321dafc71dd2e855c9e46f90d41e7fcf2c8db","tid":435850,"uid":116214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大蛇丸<br />\n集妖氣，邪氣，霸氣既角色<br />\n大部分招式都同蛇有關，幾特別</blockquote><br />\n未出疾風傳佢人氣都好高，完全係boss，但之後...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3699fb72185fa2f70b07e31b6d44fe9fd62e3852","tid":435850,"uid":116214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:51:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自來也</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同好 <br />\n阻止唔到大蛇丸變衰<br />\n師父死係自已好友大蛇丸到<br />\n最愛鋼手 唔鐘意佢<br />\n自已徒弟水門又早死 無力阻止<br />\n最後又死係自已徒弟長門手上<br />\n自來也人生表面上係三忍好威， 其實佢成個人生都充滿左無力感。。。。 有好多事情佢都無能力改變個結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁先係最痛苦<br />\n <br />\n最後死係深海中， 塵土轉生都無佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係我覺得最有血有肉的角色</blockquote><br />\n有首op 透明的世界,一開始自來也係度寫小說，成日都聽，好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3105ae8d1a1e54c1e0f0a8f6c73cc4cc5a5da1eb","tid":435850,"uid":116214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:53:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水門冇人講，好打都有限</blockquote><br />\n好多人因為佢忍界大戰既表現...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但以前佢未正式出場都勁多人鐘意，神話般既男人，比得上六道仙人，柱間，班果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3461e63500953ab8df92db16745103855218934e","tid":435850,"uid":136119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:53:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水門冇人講，好打都有限</blockquote><br />\n我咪講左囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87dfb37b08e01f74162c1824ddf4b7197fd18800","tid":435850,"uid":116214,"like":2,"disli